Peter Ivan owns a farm that keeps live stock. He uses workers to manage the farm activities
that include buying farm inputs, making sales of farm products, and recording new livestock.
You are required to develop an android application to help him ease on the process of recording
the farm activities;
The owner should be able to:
-View animals on the farm
-View workers on farm
-Register new workers
-Views performed sales
-views purchased products

The workers should be able to:
-Record new livestock information
-Record sales
-Record purchases

You are provided with an API collection having most of the methods to access some of the above requirements.
Also; the farm is located in a remote area with poor connection, so recording new records (new animals, sales
and purchases can be done offline and when the application gets good connection, the records synced in the
background
The application should implement the following concepts:
-A beautiful user interface and experience that